{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"adb228f8-d8e3-40f0-9220-df2fd989a415","content":"With **MSTest.Sdk/3.8.0**, the switch is straightforward:\n\n### In your `.csproj` / `Directory.Build.props`\n\n**Remove** (or set to `false`) the `UseVSTest` property:\n\n```xml\n<!-- Before -->\n<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>\n\n<!-- After: just delete the line -->\n```\n\nMSTest.Sdk 3.8+ defaults to **Microsoft.Testing.Platform** when `UseVSTest` is absent/false.\n\n### Other things to be aware of\n\n| Area | Change |\n|---|---|\n| **Running tests** | `dotnet test` still works; you can also run the test `.exe` directly |\n| **CLI flags** | VSTest flags like `--filter` keep working, but platform-native syntax (`--filter \"Name=Foo\"`) is also available |\n| **Runsettings** | Still supported, but some VSTest-specific adapters/extensions may need replacements |\n| **Code coverage** | If you use `--collect \"Code Coverage\"`, switch to `Microsoft.CodeCoverage` or `coverlet` configured for the new platform |\n\n### Quick validation\n\n```bash\ndotnet test --list-tests\n```\n\nIf you see output mentioning **Microsoft.Testing.Platform** (rather than the VSTest runner), the migration worked.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"55627c23-3f54-461c-aa8a-ebc7765bbc0f","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about migrating from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform in their MSTest project. This is a knowledge question about .NET testing configuration. Let me provide a concise answer based on my knowledge.\n\nWhen using MSTest.Sdk, switching from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform involves a few key changes:\n\n1. Remove `<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>` (or set it to `false`) — MSTest.Sdk 3.8+ defaults to Microsoft.Testing.Platform when this property is absent or false.\n2. The test runner invocation changes — instead of `dotnet test`, you can use `dotnet test` (which still works) or run the test executable directly.\n\n\n3. There are some differences in CLI options and how you pass arguments to the test runner.","outputTokens":510,"requestId":"982D:15489A:17CF25:1EF3C2:69FFD821"},"id":"a3cb4975-2489-467f-8c40-68e812bb0a5c","timestamp":"2026-05-10T00:58:22.228Z","parentId":"93d7aa5f-fa4d-49ea-b7f3-26c24906363b"}
